General.Name: Neodynamics AB
General.Description: NeoDynamics AB (publ), a medical technology company, develops biopsy system to enhance diagnosis and care of breast cancer patients. It develops NeoNavia, a precision biopsy system that offers clinicians and patients accurate lesion targeting and high tissue yield for correct diagnosis and individualized treatment. The company was incorporated in 2015 and is based in Lidingö, Sweden.
